ync\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8112 post__image\" src=\"/posts/washington-d-c-trip-photo-recap/img-2058-71.jpg\" alt=\"Washington D.C. Photo Recap! on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"1307\"></p>\n<p>There was a really pretty orchid display exhibit going on while we were there!</p>\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/washington-d-c-trip-photo-recap/img-2068-72.jpg\" alt=\"Washington D.C. Photo Recap! on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/washington-d-c-trip-photo-recap/img-2066-73.jpg\" alt=\"Washington D.C. Photo Recap! on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/washington-d-c-trip-photo-recap/img-2064-74.jpg\" alt=\"Washington D.C. Photo Recap! on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/washington-d-c-trip-photo-recap/img-2063-75.jpg\" alt=\"Washington D.C. Photo Recap! on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<figure id=\"attachment_8124\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8124\" style=\"width: 1326px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8124 post__image\" src=\"/posts/washington-d-c-trip-photo-recap/img-2071-76.jpg\" alt=\"Washington D.C. Photo Recap! on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"980\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8124\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Maxin & Relaxin for this little orchid.</figcaption></figure>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8123 post__image\" src=\"/posts/washington-d-c-trip-photo-recap/img-2069-77.jpg\" alt=\"Washington D.C. Photo Recap! on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"735\"></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8121 post__image\" src=\"/posts/washington-d-c-trip-photo-recap/img-2067-78.jpg\" alt=\"Washington D.C. Photo Recap! on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"1307\"></p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8159\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8159\" style=\"width: 1326px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8159 post__image\" src=\"/posts/washington-d-c-trip-photo-recap/img-3768-79.jpg\" alt=\"Washington D.C. Photo Recap! on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"980\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8159\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">How cool are these “Emerald Creepers”?! The color was amazing.</figcaption></figure>\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/washington-d-c-trip-photo-recap/img-3769-80.jpg\" alt=\"Washington D.C. Photo Recap! on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/washington-d-c-trip-photo-recap/img-3767-81.jpg\" alt=\"Washington D.C. Photo Recap! on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8104 post__image\" src=\"/posts/washington-d-c-trip-photo-recap/img-2050-82.jpg\" alt=\"Washington D.C. Photo Recap! on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"960\" height=\"960\"></p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8137\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8137\" style=\"width: 1326px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8137 post__image\" src=\"/posts/washington-d-c-trip-photo-recap/img-2114-83.jpg\" alt=\"Washington D.C. Photo Recap! on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"735\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8137\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Even the back of the Botanic Gardens were lovely!</figcaption></figure>\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/washington-d-c-trip-photo-recap/img-2113-84.jpg\" alt=\"Washington D.C. Photo Recap! on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/washington-d-c-trip-photo-recap/img-2112-85.jpg\" alt=\"Washington D.C. Photo Recap! on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<figure id=\"attachment_8134\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8134\" style=\"width: 1326px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8134 post__image\" src=\"/posts/washington-d-c-trip-photo-recap/img-2110-86.jpg\" alt=\"Washington D.C. Photo Recap! on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"980\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8134\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Hungry duckies!</figcaption></figure>\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/washington-d-c-trip-photo-recap/img-2107-87.jpg\" alt=\"Washington D.C. Photo Recap! on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/washington-d-c-trip-photo-recap/img-2108-88.jpg\" alt=\"Washington D.C. Photo Recap! on Katie Crafts; https://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8131 post__image\" src=\"/posts/washington-d-c-trip-photo-recap/img-2097-89.jpg\" alt=\"Washington D.C. Photo Recap! on Katie Crafts; http://www.katiecrafts.com\" width=\"980\" height=\"980\"></p>\n<p>It was a jam-packed mini vacation, but we had a great time! We’ll definitely go back when it’s a little less cold out. 😉</p>\n<p>Have you ever been to Washington D.C. before? What was your favorite thing to do there?</p>\n",
